item.title: CVE-2017-16110|2024-09-17T02:27:30.487Z -- hackerone -- weather.swlyons%20node%20module
item.description: weather.swlyons is a simple web server for weather updates. weather.swlyons is vulnerable to a directory traversal issue, giving an attacker access to the filesystem by placing "../" in the url.
